      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Richard Delorme</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:205px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-delorme-5b9231100/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/51/Richard_Delorme.jpg\" width=\"203\" height=\"203\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Richard_Delorme.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Richard Delorme <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Richard Delorme</b>,<br />\na French biologist working in the forest management, Ph.D. in human biology from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_Bernard_University_Lyon_1\">Claude Bernard University Lyon 1</a> in 1997 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, software developer, and games and chess programmer. He is author of the strong <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> program <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edax_(computing)\">Edax</a> written in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, also analysis engine in <a href=\"/Stephane_Nicolet\" title=\"Stephane Nicolet\">Stephane Nicolet's</a> Othello program <i>Cassio</i> for <a href=\"/Macintosh\" title=\"Macintosh\">Macintosh</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, and test-bed in <a href=\"/Deep_Learning\" title=\"Deep Learning\">deep learning</a> research <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\nRichard Delorme is furthre author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engines <a href=\"/Amoeba\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba</a> and its didactic eased counterpart <a href=\"/Dumb\" title=\"Dumb\">Dumb</a>, both written in the <a href=\"/D_(Programming_Language)\" title=\"D (Programming Language)\">D programming language</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Delorme&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Amoeba\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Amoeba#TournamentManager\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba Tournament Manager</a>, <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#SPRT\" title=\"Match Statistics\">SPRT</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dumb\" title=\"Dumb\">Dumb</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hyperbola_Quintessence\" title=\"Hyperbola Quintessence\">Hyperbola Quintessence</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Delorme&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30723\">Performance: linux vs Windows vs Mac OS X</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 21, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51272\">SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60228\">amoeba a new UCI engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 20, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62922\">sprt tourney manager</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Amoeba#TournamentManager\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba Tournament Manager</a>, <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#SPRT\" title=\"Match Statistics\">SPRT</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73625\">magic bitboard perft</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 11, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a>, <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Delorme&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo\">abulmo (Richard Delorme) · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo/amoeba\">amoeba: an UCI chess engine in D language</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo/Dumb\">Dumb: A simple &amp; stupid chess program</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo/hqperft\">hqperft: Chess move generation based on (H)yperbola (Q)uintessence &amp; range attacks</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Hyperbola_Quintessence\" title=\"Hyperbola Quintessence\">Hyperbola Quintessence</a>, <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-delorme-5b9231100\">Richard Delorme | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Delorme&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-delorme-5b9231100\">Richard Delorme | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-delorme-5b9231100\">Richard Delorme | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo/edax-reversi\">GitHub - abulmo/edax-reversi</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cassio.free.fr/\">Cassio - Play Othello on Macintosh</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Learning to Play Othello with Deep Neural Networks</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1711.06583\">arXiv:1711.06583</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/abulmo/amoeba\">GitHub - abulmo/amoeba: an UCI chess engine in d language</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65305&amp;start=2\">Re: Dumb 1.0 UCI by Richard Delorme</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 27, 2017</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301071349\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU